        "content": "## 📱 WhatsApp AI Assistant Setup\n\n**Before running:**\n1. Configure WhatsApp Business Cloud credentials\n2. Set up OpenAI API key\n3. Connect Google Calendar (for meeting scheduling)\n4. Select Google Sheets document and sheet name\n5. Populate the Knowledge Base vector store with your company data",
